Package: austalk
Title: Access Data from the Austalk Speech Corpus
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Steve",
           family = "Cassidy",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "steve.cassidy@mq.edu.au",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2357-9652"))
Description: Provides an interface to retrieve speech data from the Austalk collection 
  stored on the Alveo system.  Find speakers and filter using metadata, locate 
  recordings for each speaker and then download audio and other data. 
